            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
              <li>Use this project for one Cloudflare Pages site.</li>
              <li>Manual telemetry is the working path today.</li>
              <li>Send one metric or deployment record with service, environment, branch, and deployment ID.</li>
              <li>Store importer settings only to prepare for the future Cloudflare fetcher.</li>
